:35.000Z","msg":"大案公署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec7b00e1883e58a44ff500721dc5e44fe68adc3","tid":2038061,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7aiHLd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7aiHLd.png&h=09a6b604&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae6eb749c5b371f556cda41d642c833a8de3e83","tid":2038061,"uid":104840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔小心笑撚咗"},{"pid":"12f40e9ce4a858dcf2ec5a6e6b0016f268b252b6","tid":2038061,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02d8e1715d1dabbd4b3706095c00415d8d10ecb9","tid":2038061,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:25:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1781784/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1781784%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32bP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b042c008\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1781784%2F&h=7d1d0436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1781784/</a><br />\n<br />\n港聞 選擇分類 <br />\n廉署落案起訴3地產代理涉串謀詐騙佣金<br />\n2020-05-27 16:25 文字大小<br />\n 廉署落案起訴3地產代理涉串謀詐騙佣金<br />\n廉政公署今日落案起訴一名前任及兩名現任地產代理，控告他們涉嫌訛稱其中一人有份參與一宗住宅物業租賃交易，串謀詐騙一間物業代理公司佣金5400元。3名被告已獲廉署准予保釋，將於星期五(29日)在西九龍裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n郭淑賢，49歲，中原地產代理有限公司(中原地產)前地產代理；朱康聯，34歲，及黃育強，34歲，均為中原地產的地產代理，同被控一項串謀詐騙罪名，違反普通法。廉署早前接獲貪污投訴，調查後揭發上述涉嫌罪行。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告於案發時任職中原地產的地產代理，郭淑賢及朱康聯負責促成物業交易，而黃育強是他們的上司。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指郭淑賢、朱康聯及黃育強涉嫌於2018年7月25日至8月17日期間，一同串謀欺詐中原地產，不誠實地向該公司虛假地表示，朱康聯為2018年7月一宗涉及大角咀一個住宅物業的租賃交易的洽商者，因而誘使及導致中原地產向朱康聯支付逾5400元的佣金。<br />\n<br />\n據報3名被告的虛假陳述，導致中原額外支付佣金逾2200元。中原地產在廉署調查案件期間提供全面協助。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"屌你個標題<br />\n世紀大案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8cd180aa90ead698bd03e8e5414d41acd5f73d","tid":2038061,"uid":114019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449679dad8a51b5abd25008d2ee94a3e50087693","tid":2038061,"uid":216780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"猶如垃圾<br />\n養班仆街"},{"pid":"0e15a86b2304e147d7f407ef1b6756152d26be83","tid":2038061,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢啦"},{"pid":"a08878f33dce65010d7e0f87c6e58c2b726acaf4","tid":2038061,"uid":228842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"icac笑話"},{"pid":"f532aaf38d26e1a49df80fbc5511c001cfcf5228","tid":2038061,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ca61f241bb44de8cfc201c098229d61bd65ec0b","tid":2038061,"uid":145837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e85fff9df9c4d32b5ea07a99299a896321acbe6","tid":2038061,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6a1c85d3abbbda0a6f2c929581f22f348abb64f8","tid":2038061,"uid":179409,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"算吧啦<br />\nICAC依家個名仲衰過食環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食環都有人鬧<br />\nICAC直情俾人覺得係解散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"ICAC 好型wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:09:11.000Z","msg":"型條撚<br />\n你咁講，渠務處仲型啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"ICAC 有槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />